        "gg-EMC2AYnn_childItem_0": "<p>Benefit</p>",
        "gg-EMC2AYnn_childItem_1": "<p>Key ingredients</p>",
        "gg-EMC2AYnn_childItem_2": "<p>How to take</p>",
        "gg-EMC2AYnn_childItem_3": "<p>How long before I see results?</p>",
        "gg-EMC2AYnn_childItem_4": "<p>Money Back Guarantee</p>",
        "gg2646ZTVHg_text": "<p>Astaxanthin 12 mg</p>",
        "gg7D5_4Nq0J_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">Astaxanthin is fat-soluble, meaning absorption may be improved with the presence of dietary fats. Published research shows that lipid-based formulations support astaxanthin absorption compared to dry powder capsules.* Organic coconut oil is included to support bioavailability.*</span></p>",
        "ggA9Bg6luda_text": "<p>Absorption support:</p>",
        "ggB5PzeHDV6_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">Individual results vary.*</span>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggB8uNth_Mr_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://tryrovina.com/cdn/shop/files/UGC_image_b1ee8ad2-e23c-4c34-8bda-123b50c32409.jpg?v=1769327286",
        "ggCHw4Ua8Q-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/payment-icons-shopify-701751695132514cid24jj9av-removebg-preview.png",
        "ggFRrGPlRvn_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">We recommend consistent use for at least 4-6 weeks to allow your body to fully adapt.* Because this supplement supports wellness at the cellular level, consistent use is recommended.*</span></p>",
        "ggHrjpAuMiP_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ No artificial colors</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ No flavors or preservatives</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ Non-GMO</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ Gluten-free</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ Soy-free</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">✓ No fillers or unnecessary additives</span></p>",
        "ggJiKutB-xb_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(31,31,31);\"><strong>Cellular Energy Support – </strong>Supports daily vitality from within*</span></p>",
        "ggJmKcQ09MV_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Multi-System Support – </strong>Works across your whole body</span></p>",
        "ggLGulN0zro_text": "<p>4.<strong> Works with or without lifestyle changes</strong> - Simply add to your daily routine</p>",
        "ggLJAvSJglo_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">Published research on oral astaxanthin shows that skin improvements have been documented within 6-8 weeks of consistent daily use in clinical studies. In some studies, measurable changes in skin carotenoid levels were observed within 3-4 weeks.*</span></p>",
        "ggMXJieDh0b_text": "<p><strong>Official Store Notice</strong></p>",
        "ggOdNmHUyZa_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">If you're not 100% satisfied within the first 90 days, just send it back to us and we'll give you a full refund</span></p>",
        "ggPD5Sbeolm_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(43,43,43);\">90-day money-back guarantee</span></p>",
        "ggPJCN06EMw_text": "<p>1.<strong> Take 4 softgel daily, 2 in the morning and 2 in the evening</strong></p>",
        "ggR57JxTVpJ_text": "<p>3. <strong>Continue daily for ongoing benefits </strong>- Long-term cellular protection and wellness</p>",
        "ggR9YOVuPoO_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">*</span><strong>Contains Krill (crustacean shellfish).</strong><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\"> Not suitable for those with shellfish allergies.</span></p>",
        "ggT-d9qEQMz_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">Astaxanthin is uniquely structured to interact with both the inner and outer layers of the cell membrane, which may allow for more comprehensive cellular support compared to other antioxidants.*</span></p>",
        "ggT9sSQekkq_errorMessage": "Cannot add product to cart",
        "ggT9sSQekkq_label": "Add to cart",
        "ggT9sSQekkq_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
