        "ggpfp1iflqA_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(18,18,18);\">Astaxanthin is a marine carotenoid that has been evaluated in over 70 peer-reviewed human clinical studies.* When taken consistently at the 12mg dose — the amount used in multiple clinical trials - it may support multiple body systems over time.*</span></p>",
