        "gglq-8T_6Q-_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgba(46,42,57,0.9);\">Sourced from Haematococcus pluvialis microalgae, this 12mg dose delivers one of nature's most potent antioxidants, designed for daily, long-term cellular support.*</span></p>",
