        "gg1VwC9y7eK_text": "<p>Trusted by 100,000+ customers and backed by our 90-day money-back guarantee.</p>",
        "gg68d1v13B8_text": "<p>Astaxanthin is recognized as one of the most powerful antioxidants available. Research shows it is:</p>",
        "ggAOotfBZ3W_text": "<p>✔ Natural microalgae source<br>✔ Oil-based for absorption<br>✔ No fillers or unnecessary additives</p>",
        "ggIAgbhetnC_text": "The Strongest Antioxidant",
        "ggN2jayCGvf_childItem_0": "<p>Antioxidant Strength</p>",
        "ggN2jayCGvf_childItem_1": "<p>What's Inside</p>",
        "ggN2jayCGvf_childItem_2": "<p>Why It Works</p>",
        "ggNcltdnZGf_text": "<p>...at neutralizing free radicals that contribute to cellular aging, oxidative stress, and declining wellness.</p>",
        "ggQgOm34h-z_text": "<p>The natural extraction process preserves the compound's antioxidant integrity while our oil-based delivery system ensures optimal absorption, making it suitable for consistent daily use without harsh additives or synthetic alternatives.</p>",
        "ggTCbphmHO-_text": "<p>Unlike most antioxidants, astaxanthin protects both the inner and outer layers of the cell membrane. This allows it to defend cells more completely against oxidative stress from environmental factors, daily demands, and natural aging processes.</p>",
        "ggUG_xUkpbV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/5ce46524-3b42-41d9-a702-5bdb0d3589f8.jpg",
        "ggUG_xUkpbV_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/5ce46524-3b42-41d9-a702-5bdb0d3589f8.jpg",
        "ggUG_xUkpbV_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/Untitled_design_29.webp",
        "ggUjVFTnDGC_text": "<p>Astaxanthin has been extensively studied as part of nutritional research focused on cellular health, antioxidant activity, and overall wellness. Rovina delivers a 12mg dose in a convenient softgel format.</p>",
        "ggW6qHAJkWd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/Heart_Research.webp",
        "ggXzncLQzL6_text": "One Pure Ingredient",
        "ggZAk96Tt6d_text": "<p>Designed for long-term wellness, not quick fixes.</p>",
        "ggZCg0_yN_6_text": "Backed by Research &amp; Results",
        "ggeFAUbFmRl_text": "<p>Many supplements rely on complex blends and proprietary formulas. We keep it simple. Pure astaxanthin from microalgae, nothing unnecessary.</p>",
        "ggi1kUqf_7A_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0824/3976/6260/files/Untitled_design_29.webp",
        "ggjJ1rPkOpG_text": "<p>This level of protection is why benefits build over time instead of fading.</p>",
        "ggtvzuDt2PF_childItem_0": "<p>6,000x stronger than Vitamin C</p>",
        "ggtvzuDt2PF_childItem_1": "<p>800x stronger than CoQ10</p>",
        "ggtvzuDt2PF_childItem_2": "<p>550x stronger than Vitamin E</p>",
        "ggtvzuDt2PF_childItem_3": "<p>75x stronger than Alpha Lipoic Acid</p>",
        "ggujSuAIR17_text": "<strong>Discover Why Experts Trust Rovina Astaxanthin</strong>"
